DIGEST OF HB 1417 (Updated February 18, 2026 6:59 pm - DI 149)
Citations Affected: IC 4-3; IC 34-6; IC 34-11.
Synopsis: Causes of action and damages. Establishes a tort reform
commission. Limits a civil cause of action concerning a public
nuisance.
Effective: Upon passage; July 1, 2026.
Lehman, Snow, Pressel,
Zimmerman
(SENATE SPONSORS — BALDWIN, GARTEN)
