January 29, 2026, read second time, ordered engrossed.
January 30, 2026, engrossed.
February 2, 2026, read third time, passed. Yeas 61, nays 34.
SENATE ACTION
February 5, 2026, read first time and referred to Committee on Judiciary.
February 19, 2026, amended, reported favorably — Do Pass.
